@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "Wonder Watch Privacy Policy. Understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information with absolute discretion.";
}

<section class="pt-[136px] pb-[96px] px-[32px] md:px-[64px] max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-[64px] border-b border-white-faint pb-[48px]">
        <span class="font-sans font-bold text-[10px] text-gold tracking-[3.3px] uppercase mb-[16px] block">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-[48px] md:text-[64px] text-parchment leading-none tracking-[-1.5px] mb-[16px]">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-muted">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[48px] font-sans text-[15px] text-muted leading-[1.75]">

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gold-faint p-[24px] relative">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-l border-gold/40 m-3 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-r border-gold/40 m-3 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-parchment leading-relaxed">
                <span class="text-gold font-bold">Our Core Commitment:</span> Wonder Watch operates on a foundation of absolute client discretion. We collect only what is necessary, share nothing without your consent, and treat your personal information with the same reverence we apply to the timepieces we curate.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="mb-[16px]">We collect information you voluntarily provide during account registration, purchases, and communications, including:</p>
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[8px] pl-0">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Full name, email address, and phone number</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Billing and shipping addresses</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Payment transaction references (we do not store card details — these are handled by Razorpay)</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Order and acquisition history</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Device and browsing data for platform performance purposes</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-[16px]">Your information is used solely to:</p>
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[8px] pl-0">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Process and fulfil your acquisitions</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Send transactional communications (order confirmations, shipping updates)</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Deliver the Wonder Watch Journal (if you have opted in)</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Maintain account security and fraud prevention</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Improve platform performance and user experience</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">3. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data under any circumstances. We may share minimal data with trusted third-party service providers (Razorpay for payments, courier partners for shipping) strictly to fulfil your order. These providers are bound by their own privacy standards and are contractually prohibited from using your data for any other purpose.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">4. Data Security</h2>
            <p>All data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.3. Payment information is processed exclusively by Razorpay (PCI DSS Level 1 compliant). Your passwords are hashed using industry-standard algorithms and are never stored in plain text. We conduct regular security audits of our infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="mb-[16px]">In accordance with the Information Technology (Amendment) Act 2008 and applicable data protection guidelines, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[8px] pl-0">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Access a copy of the personal data we hold about you</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Request deletion of your account and associated data via your Vault profile</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-[12px]"><span class="text-gold mt-[4px]">—</span><span>Opt out of marketing communications at any time</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">6. Contact</h2>
            <p>For any privacy-related requests or questions, please contact our Data Privacy Officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@wonderwatch.in" class="text-gold hover:text-parchment transition-colors">privacy@wonderwatch.in</a>. We will respond within 5 business days.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>
